POSTFACTS


= version 0, Dave Morano

This was the initial release back in the early 1990s.


= version 0a, Dave Morano 00/01/19

This version added file logging and user file maintenance.  Also, the
program (nominally RBBPOST) and a newsgroup for it, the program
(nominally MSGS) and a spooldir for it, are configurable from the
PCS-wide configuration file.  Also, the mailer name to put in the mail
header postmarks is configurable from both the invocation arguments and
the PCS-wide configuration file.



